comment:
this lawyer lost cause he thought he was smart. he is clearly trying to go against the rules of evidence. 

so to break this down for you i law the law of evidence is split into two sections Relevancy and Admissibility. Under admissibility for character evidence, it is generally INADMISSIBLE. that means u cannot bring up your own good character  or your opponents bad character traits unless IT BECOMES A LIVE ISSUE. So what did her lawyer do wrong? he made (Bitch) character an issue when he noted that (bitch) spoke publicly about her alleged DomesticV and thus separation with JD. this in itself is bringing up your opponent's Bad Character. thus this becomes a live issue and both parties can visit the topic as it is now relevant issue of contention. That is basically what this entire case is about. Now (bitch) lawyer went even further by saying she donated all the money to a charity. this would be a direct implication that (bitch) is of good character, and by the rules of evidence you now know that since u brought it up both parties are now entitled to visit the issue. 

(bitch) lawyer refusing to allow JD lawyer to visit this is a direct violation against the laws of evidence and as obviously the judge is not going to sit well with this. He also made the mistake of trying to force the proceedings to be adjourned for the purposes of transferring proceedings. what this action represents is an ousting of jurisdiction of the court without valid reason. and i dont think i have to breakdown what an insult that is to any judge presiding over that case huh.
